### Hadith 2:15

*Narrated 'Aisha:*

AbdurRahman bin Abi Bakr came holding a Siwak with which he was cleaning
his teeth. Allah's Apostle looked at him. I requested Abdur-Rahman to
give the Siwak to me and after he gave it to me I divided it, chewed it
and gave it to Allah's Apostle. Then he cleaned his teeth with it and
(at that time) he was resting against my chest.

